		<h4>Overview:</h4>
		<p>
			The app is meant to time how long you take in the shower and
			then day by day it will subtract a minute from your time until
			you reach the goal which is 8 minutes. So that means that you
			will only use 16 gallons each time you shower. There are ways
			to earn points and compete with other people. When you reach
			your goal you will receive a trophy to add to your collection.
		</p>
		<img src="https://blueplanetnetwork.org/img/whywater5.jpg">

